import {
  Box,
  Card,
  CardBody,
  CardHeader,
  Center,
  Heading,
  Stack,
  StackDivider,
  Text,
  Image,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import React from "react";

const Landing = () => {
  return (
    <Center h="100vh" flexDir="column" w="full">
      <Card align="center" rounded="2xl">
        <CardHeader>
          <Center flexDir="column" gap={5}>
            <Box w="75%" position="relative">
              <Image
                alt="logo"
                boxSize="60px"
                shadow="base"
                rounded="lg"
                src="logo192.png"
              />
              <Box
                position="absolute"
                top="calc(-20%)"
                w="full"
                left="calc(-50vw + 50%)"
                height="calc(100%)"
                background="radial-50% 50% at center, transparent 10%, white 100%)"
                backgroundImage={"/home-ui-bg.svg"}
                //background="radial-gradient(50% 50% at center, transparent 10%, white 100%), url(home-ui-bg.svg)"
              />
              <Image
                alt="logo"
                boxSize="60px"
                shadow="base"
                rounded="lg"
                src="home-ui-bg.png"
              />
            </Box>

            <Heading size="md">Welcome</Heading>
          </Center>
        </CardHeader>

        <CardBody>
          <Stack divider={<StackDivider />} spacing="4">
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Summary
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                View a summary of all your clients over the last month.
              </Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Overview
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                Check out the overview of your clients.
              </Text>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Heading size="xs" textTransform="uppercase">
                Analysis
              </Heading>
              <Text pt="2" fontSize="sm">
                See a detailed analysis of all your business clients.
              </Text>
            </Box>
          </Stack>
        </CardBody>
      </Card>
    </Center>
  );
};

export default Landing;
